<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="312" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="23.[828,1437,190,853]" pageId="23" pageNumber="312">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[828,955,702,726]" pageId="23" pageNumber="312">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named after Jean Guillaume Audinet-Serville (1775–1858), the great French entomologist and coauthor of ‘ 
<emphasis box="[872,1366,766,789]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="312">Histoire naturelle des insectes Hémiptères</emphasis>
’ with C. J.-B. Amyot.
</paragraph>
